    "status" : "extensions",
    "div" : "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ValueSet tiflow-erezept-operation-outcome-details-vs</b></p><a name=\"tiflow-erezept-operation-outcome-details-vs\"> </a><a name=\"hctiflow-erezept-operation-outcome-details-vs\"> </a><p>This value set includes codes based on the following rules:</p><ul><li>Include all codes defined in <a href=\"CodeSystem-tiflow-erezept-operation-outcome-details-cs.html\"><code>https://gematik.de/fhir/erp/CodeSystem/tiflow-erezept-operation-outcome-details-cs</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated, which means it is fixed to the version provided in this specification\"> version &#x1F4E6;1.0.0-draft</span></li><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html\"><code>https://gematik.de/fhir/tiflow/core/CodeSystem/tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated, which means it is fixed to the version provided in this specification\"> version &#x1F4E6;1.0.0-draft</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_AUTH_ROLE_NOT_ALLOWED\">TIFLOW_AUTH_ROLE_NOT_ALLOWED</a></td><td>Access role not allowed</td><td>The authenticated actor role is not permitted to execute this operation</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_SECRET_MISMATCH\">TIFLOW_SECRET_MISMATCH</a></td><td>Task secret mismatch</td><td>The provided task secret does not match the secret stored for the task</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_TASK_STATUS_MISMATCH\">TIFLOW_TASK_STATUS_MISMATCH</a></td><td>Task status mismatch</td><td>The task is in a status that does not allow execution of this operation</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_MEDICATION_DISPENSE_INVALID\">TIFLOW_MEDICATION_DISPENSE_INVALID</a></td><td>MedicationDispense invalid</td><td>The provided MedicationDispense resource is invalid for this operation</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_MEDICATION_DISPENSE_MISSING\">TIFLOW_MEDICATION_DISPENSE_MISSING</a></td><td>MedicationDispense missing</td><td>A required MedicationDispense resource is missing for this operation</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_SIGNATURE_NO_OCSP_RESPONSE\">TIFLOW_SIGNATURE_NO_OCSP_RESPONSE</a></td><td>No OCSP response for signature</td><td>Certificate revocation status could not be determined because no OCSP response was available</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_AUTH_NOT_OWNER\">TIFLOW_AUTH_NOT_OWNER</a></td><td>Authenticated actor is not owner</td><td>The authenticated actor is not the owner of the addressed task</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_ACCESSCODE_MISMATCH\">TIFLOW_ACCESSCODE_MISMATCH</a></td><td>Access code mismatch</td><td>The provided access code does not match the access code assigned to the task</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_TASK_ID_REQUIRED\">TIFLOW_TASK_ID_REQUIRED</a></td><td>Task id required</td><td>The operation requires a task id in the request</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_KVNR_MISMATCH\">TIFLOW_KVNR_MISMATCH</a></td><td>KVNR mismatch</td><td>The KVNR in the request does not match the KVNR assigned to the task context</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_SIGNATURE_INVALID_ISSUING_ROLE\">TIFLOW_SIGNATURE_INVALID_ISSUING_ROLE</a></td><td>Signature issuing role invalid</td><td>The signature was created by an actor role that is not allowed for the signed artifact</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_FLOWTYPE_MISMATCH\">TIFLOW_FLOWTYPE_MISMATCH</a></td><td>Flow type mismatch</td><td>The task flow type does not match the expected flow for this operation</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_COVERAGE_TYPE_MISMATCH\">TIFLOW_COVERAGE_TYPE_MISMATCH</a></td><td>Coverage type mismatch</td><td>The coverage type does not match the expected coverage context</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_CERTIFICATE_INVALID\">TIFLOW_CERTIFICATE_INVALID</a></td><td>Certificate invalid</td><td>The certificate used for authentication or signature validation is invalid</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_OCSP_BACKEND_ERROR\">TIFLOW_OCSP_BACKEND_ERROR</a></td><td>Invalid OCSP response</td><td>Failed to retrieve the OCSP response for the certificate of the signature</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_SIGNATURE_INVALID\">TIFLOW_SIGNATURE_INVALID</a></td><td>Signature invalid</td><td>The digital signature is invalid or cannot be verified</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_KVNR_INVALID\">TIFLOW_KVNR_INVALID</a></td><td>KVNR invalid</td><td>The provided KVNR is invalid or does not conform to the expected format</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_SIGNATURE_AUTHOREDON_MISMATCH\">TIFLOW_SIGNATURE_AUTHOREDON_MISMATCH</a></td><td>Signature authoredOn mismatch</td><td>The authoredOn timestamp does not match the signed content</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_IKNR_INVALID\">TIFLOW_IKNR_INVALID</a></td><td>IKNR invalid</td><td>The provided IKNR is invalid or not accepted in this context</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_LANR_ZANR_INVALID\">TIFLOW_LANR_ZANR_INVALID</a></td><td>LANR or ZANR invalid</td><td>The provided LANR or ZANR is invalid or not accepted for this operation</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_TASK_DELETED\">TIFLOW_TASK_DELETED</a></td><td>Task deleted</td><td>The task was already cancelled or deleted and can no longer be processed</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_TASK_EXPIRED\">TIFLOW_TASK_EXPIRED</a></td><td>Task expired</td><td>The task cannot be processed because its redemption period has expired</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_MESSAGE_TO_SELF\">TIFLOW_MESSAGE_TO_SELF</a></td><td>Message to self not allowed</td><td>A communication message addressed to the sender itself is not permitted</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_COMMUNICATION_PAYLOAD_INVALID\">TIFLOW_COMMUNICATION_PAYLOAD_INVALID</a></td><td>Communication payload invalid</td><td>The communication payload is syntactically or semantically invalid</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_INSURANT_NOT_ELIGIBLE\">TIFLOW_INSURANT_NOT_ELIGIBLE</a></td><td>Insurant not eligible</td><td>The insurant does not meet the eligibility constraints for this communication flow</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_RECIPIENT_INVALID\">TIFLOW_RECIPIENT_INVALID</a></td><td>Recipient invalid</td><td>The specified recipient is invalid for the requested communication</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_TASK_NOT_FOUND\">TIFLOW_TASK_NOT_FOUND</a></td><td>Task not found</td><td>The referenced task does not exist</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_MVO_NOT_VALID_YET\">TIFLOW_MVO_NOT_VALID_YET</a></td><td>MVO not valid yet</td><td>The multi-prescription is not yet valid at the current point in time</td></tr></table></li><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"https://simplifier.net/resolve?scope=de.gematik.epa.medication@1.3.0&amp;canonical=https://gematik.de/fhir/ti/CodeSystem/operation-outcome-details-codes\"><code>https://gematik.de/fhir/ti/CodeSystem/operation-outcome-details-codes</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated, which means it is fixed to 1.1.1, the version found through the package references\"> version &#x1F4E6;1.1.1</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"https://simplifier.net/resolve?scope=de.gematik.epa.medication@1.3.0&amp;canonical=https://gematik.de/fhir/ti/CodeSystem/operation-outcome-details-codes#operation-outcome-details-codes-SVC_VALIDATION_FAILED\">SVC_VALIDATION_FAILED</a></td><td>FHIR Profile Validation Failed</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"https://simplifier.net/resolve?scope=de.gematik.epa.medication@1.3.0&amp;canonical=https://gematik.de/fhir/ti/CodeSystem/operation-outcome-details-codes#operation-outcome-details-codes-SVC_IDENTITY_MISMATCH\">SVC_IDENTITY_MISMATCH</a></td><td>Identity mismatch: Access token or x-insurantid header does not match FHIR data (Telematik-ID / KVNR)</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"https://simplifier.net/resolve?scope=de.gematik.epa.medication@1.3.0&amp;canonical=https://gematik.de/fhir/ti/CodeSystem/operation-outcome-details-codes#operation-outcome-details-codes-SVC_TELEMATIKID_TEMPORARILY_BLOCKED\">SVC_TELEMATIKID_TEMPORARILY_BLOCKED</a></td><td>The specified Telematik-ID is temporarily blocked</td></tr></table></li></ul></div>"
